3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with modeling and predicting physical interactions, which is a common problem in AI. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper demonstrates the use of the proposed model for model-based control in a task with interacting objects. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with modeling and predicting the dynamics of physical systems.
